eprints.title: Dataset supporting the publication "Reef-building corals farm and feed on their photosynthetic symbionts".
eprints.abstract: Dataset supporting the publication by Wiedenmann, J. et al. "Reef-building corals farm and feed on their photosynthetic symbionts". Nature (2023). https://doi.org/10.1038/s41586-023-06442-5 This dataset contains all the raw data used in the paper cited above, organised within five worksheets in an excel file: Wiedenmann et al_Repository.xlsx Worksheets are labelled as: - Coral growth_10 species - Mean Grey Value_Calibration - N15 enrichment experiments - N-P acquisition - Chagos N15 and Growth Data This project was supported by NERC (NE/T001364/1)
